---
title: Midwest Chorizo 'n' Fixins Tacos with Cheddar and Crema
description: All the fun of the yellow box, homemade at your dinner table! Saucy and flavourful chorizo tops warm tortillas along with anything you love on your tacos! Like raw onions on your tacos? Keep some aside before cooking the rest with the chorizo and seasonings.
